item.title: Thrive - Rising Above Disappointment
item.description: Welcome to Odessa First Assembly's Podcast, where each week, we bring you powerful sermons and messages that inspire, encourage, and deepen your connection with God. Join us as we explore the Scriptures together, seeking wisdom and understanding for our daily lives. Follow us on social media @odessafirstag for updates, and if you'd like to support our ministry, visit odessafirst.com/giving. Thank you for tuning in and growing with us on this faith journey!
